item.title: 3D Fashion Design
item.dc:creator: binh002tn
item.description:
Some outstanding features of the software:
  • Design costumes with 3D images.
  • Simple interface, easy to use.
  • Develop ideas in clothing design.
  • Integrated tools make it easy to edit and change designs easily.
Note: You can use the software for free for 30 days. After that, you have to pay 1,100,000 VND/1 month, 9,900,000 VND/1 year to continue using.

item.title: Nike Yoga Dri-FIT
item.dc:creator: binh002tn
item.description: Move with ease in 360 degrees of comfort and support in these high-waisted leggings. Soft, sweat-wicking fabric stretches with you effortlessly while you flow through your poses. Colour-blocked panelling and curved seam lines follow your shape for a sleek look as you bend and reach. This product is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.
item.content:encoded: Move with ease in 360 degrees of comfort and support in these high-waisted leggings. Soft, sweat-wicking fabric stretches with you effortlessly while you flow through your poses. Colour-blocked panelling and curved seam lines follow your shape for a sleek look as you bend and reach. This product is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.
